<br>
Some players are very good at taunting no matter what they wield for a weapon, while others will struggle even with EB procing weapons.<br>
<br>
It all boils down to Timeing and Sequence and being Sexor. The more sexor you are the more the mob hates you for looking good. and some people will never figure it out no matter what you tell them.  Its like breathing, you just know when.<br>
<br>
Also all players have a responciblity to control taunt, however there will always be a smartass that will say hummm i am more uber than you lets make your job difficult.<br>
<br>
Time your taunting with weapon hits, followed by slam.  If you do not have slam then try kick.  Good 1 hand and Good 2 hand weapons are about equal.  My preference for a 2 Handed weapon over 1 handed weapon.<br>
<br>
If that does not work you could always be a shaman.<br>
<br>
